						<summary>

						<p>Stone fixed into the sluices of the tank called Doṅgala-Cheruvu.</p>						

						<p>It mentions the Collector's Jamādār, Mīre Sāhebu Ijaradār Gaphūra Sāhēbu, Vengala-Reḍḍi and another person. In late characters.</p>						

